<!--BPEC BEGIN-->

<div class="row bpec">
  <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
    <img src="images/build.png" class="add-top" height="100px"/>
    <h2><b>BUILD</b></h2>
    <p>Create structures, working machines, whole new worlds with 3Scape. Let us springboard your ideas into the 3D world!
      The possibilites are endless! The only limit is your imagination...</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
    <img src="images/play.png" class="add-top" height="100px"/>
    <h2><b>PLAY</b></h2>
    <p>We strive to make 3Scape as fun as possible. This allows you to have the freedom to do anything you want.
    If you want to make a catapult and knock down some walls do it! If you want to have a dragon fly around and fight robots do it!
    This world is your playground, have some fun!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
    <img src="images/experiment.png" class="add-top" height="100px"/>
    <h2><b>EXPERIMENT</b></h2>
    <p>Here at 3Scape, we encourage experimentation. If something seems even slightly possible, try it! Our engine has a great deal of flexibility
    and can do some pretty amazing things. Pretty much every day we discover something new we didn't know we could do, and we built this!
    Feel free to share with us your cool projects and experiments, we love learning new things!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
    <img src="images/code.png" class="add-top" height="100px"/>
    <h2><b>CODE</b></h2>
    <p>Coding is slowly becoming a way of life these days and because of that, we encourage everyone to learn how to do basic coding.
      3Scape is built in such a way that if you are comfortable building things through code, you can do so! 3Scape is flexible and fully
      accesible to those who want to get their hands dirty, the coder's way!</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!--BPEC END-->


</body>
</html>
